data.description: Welcome Home! This updated chic Rambler has everything you want. A cozy 3 bedrooms, 1 spacious and renovated bathroom complimented by beautiful granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances in the kitchen.   Come and enjoy the open concept great room - perfect for family gatherings! A covered enclosed deck w/ wet bar for multi-purpose use extends your living space by 144 sq ft. This home shows well and lives even better!   Close to transportation, shops, and major routes.  Note: This home qualifies potential buyers for up to $10,000 or a 3% down payment and/or closing cost assistance. The borrower must meet all first trust guidelines, income restrictions, and census tract requirements.  Recently appraised well above asking.   Please contact the listing agent for details.
